                      },
                      {
                        "kind": "text",
                        "text": " input points are necessary.  If the\ninput is longer than this, it is cropped.  If it is shorter than this,\nit is padded with zeros.  If "
                      },
                      {
                        "kind": "code",
                        "text": "n"
                      },
                      {
                        "kind": "text",
                        "text": " is not given, it is taken to be\n"
                      },
